snippet.title: The Symmetry of a Snowflake
snippet.description:
A hastily made and underprepared video about snowflakes.

For more details and better information, check out snowcrystals.com http://www.its.caltech.edu/~atomic/snowcrystals/

And have a look at last year's 'snow chemistry' by periodicvideos - and subscribe! http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wuPTPUkTQ7s
